  },
  {
    question: "What financing options are available for Oakville waterproofing?",
    answer: "We offer multiple financing solutions for Oakville homeowners: 0% interest financing for 12 months through our lending partners (subject to credit approval), extended payment plans up to 60 months, and coordination with home equity lines of credit. Many Oakville banks and credit unions offer home improvement loans at competitive rates (currently 6-8%), and waterproofing qualifies as a capital improvement that increases home value. For seniors, the Ontario Seniors' Home Safety Tax Credit provides up to $2,500 annually for eligible modifications. CMHC Green Home programs may offer grants or low-interest loans for waterproofing combined with energy efficiency upgrades. We provide detailed invoices and warranty documentation needed for all financing applications."
  },
  {
    question: "What warranty do you provide on Oakville waterproofing work?",
    answer: "All DrySpace basement waterproofing in Oakville includes a comprehensive 25-year transferable warranty covering materials and workmanship. This covers exterior membranes, drainage systems, sump pumps, and all installation work. The warranty is fully transferable to future homeowners (valuable for resale in Oakville's competitive real estate market) and includes annual inspection options. For heritage properties, we provide additional documentation of heritage-compliant materials and methods. Our warranty is backed by $5 million liability insurance and WSIB coverage. We're a local GTA company that's been serving Oakville since 2008 — we'll be here to honor our warranty decades from now."
